OL,3,C'Broken forever': Mum of woman killed
OL,4,Cby man arrested nine times
OL,6,FPaul Crowther, the man responsible,
OL,7,Fhad been arrested nine times under the
OL,8,FMental Health Act. He had previously
OL,9,Fbeen violent towards at least two
OL,10,Fother partners. Three people had
OL,11,Freported him to police in the three
OL,12,Fweeks before Bethany's murder for
OL,13,Fviolent behaviour.
OL,15,FBethany herself had been to West
OL,16,FYorkshire Police in August 2019 to
OL,17,Freport her fears that he would hurt
OL,18,Fher.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/19
