OL,3,C'Broken forever': Mum of woman killed
OL,4,Cby man arrested nine times
OL,6,FBethany - described by her mother as
OL,7,F"a beautiful soul, a beautiful young
OL,8,Flady" - met Crowther in 2017. They
OL,9,Fmoved in together in March 2018.
OL,11,FShe tried to help him with
OL,12,Flongstanding mental health problems
OL,13,Fbut, in June 2019, she ended the
OL,14,Frelationship because of his abusive
OL,15,Fbehaviour and his constant threats
OL,16,Ftowards her and her friends.
OL,18,FIt later became clear that the abuse
OL,19,Fshe suffered mirrored that experienced
OL,20,Fby two of Crowther's previous victims.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/19
