OL,6,FCrowther then drove to a bridge and
OL,7,Fthreatened to kill himself before he
OL,8,Fwas arrested.
OL,10,FMs Jones recalled finding out after
OL,11,Fbeing called to attend a police
OL,12,Fstation.
OL,14,F"I went into this room and I just kept
OL,15,Fsaying 'Tell me, just please, please,
OL,16,Fplease tell me she's alright'," she
OL,17,Fsaid.
