OL,6,F"They said the words I'll never
OL,7,Fforget: 'Your daughter did not survive
OL,8,Fher injuries'. And I just said:
OL,9,F'What's he done?' I said 'It's that
OL,10,FPaul Crowther isn't it?'
OL,12,F"They hung their heads in shame and I
OL,13,Fsaid: 'She came to you for help'. And
OL,14,Fthey put their heads down."
