OL,3,C'Broken forever': Mum of woman killed
OL,4,Cby man arrested nine times
OL,6,FCrowther eventually pleaded guilty to
OL,7,FBethany's manslaughter by diminished
OL,8,Fresponsibility on the basis of his
OL,9,Fmental health problems and was given a
OL,10,Fhospital order, including life
OL,11,Fimprisonment with a minimum term of 12
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,FAn investigation by ITV Calendar has
OL,15,Ffound that Bethany was one of at least
OL,16,F18 women killed by a partner, ex-
OL,17,Fpartner or family member between 2019
OL,18,Fand 2023 who were already known to
OL,19,Fpolice.
