OL,6,FAt least 15 of those women had gone to
OL,7,Fthe police themselves. At least four
OL,8,Fof the men were on bail at the time
OL,9,Fthey committed the offence.
OL,11,F'Gross failings, neglect, lack of duty
OL,12,Fof care'
OL,14,FA domestic homicide review carried out
OL,15,Fafter Bethany's death found a series
OL,16,Fof missed opportunities to address
OL,17,FPaul Crowther's worrying behaviour.
