OL,3,C'Broken forever': Mum of woman killed
OL,4,Cby man arrested nine times
OL,6,FHis background meant he "met the
OL,7,Fdefinition of a serial perpetrator of
OL,8,Fdomestic abuse" at the time Bethany
OL,9,Fmet him, the review said, but "this
OL,10,Fwas not recognised by agencies until
OL,11,Fafter he killed Bethany".
OL,13,FCrowther had a long history of
OL,14,Fproblems.
OL,16,FHis mother told the review he was
OL,17,Fexcluded from school as a result of
OL,18,F"going for a teacher", had regular
OL,19,F"meltdowns" and was violent towards
OL,20,Fone of his sisters.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/19
