OL,3,C'Broken forever': Mum of woman killed
OL,4,Cby man arrested nine times
OL,6,FHe was convicted of harassing another
OL,7,Fwoman.
OL,9,FIn total, the force held 15
OL,10,Fsafeguarding records relating to
OL,11,FCrowther in relation domestic abuse
OL,12,Fdating back to 2000, although in some
OL,13,Finstances he was recorded as the
OL,14,Falleged victim.
OL,16,FOn the national police database he was
OL,17,Fflagged with "warning markers" for
OL,18,Fviolence, mental health, suicidal
OL,19,Fthoughts and self`harm.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/19
