OL,6,FIn one instance he had allegedly
OL,7,Fstabbed an off-duty police community
OL,8,Fsupport officer in the leg.
OL,10,FThere were also multiple records of
OL,11,Fcontact between Crowther and health
OL,12,Fservices, as well as police, about his
OL,13,Fown mental health.
OL,15,FBethany had been in contact with Leeds
OL,16,FDomestic Violence Service as early as
OL,17,F2018 because of concerns about
OL,18,FCrowther.
