OL,6,FOn 12 August 2019 she was taken by a
OL,7,Ffriend to a police station in Leeds to
OL,8,Freport threats he had made against her.
OL,10,FThe friend told the review Bethany was
OL,11,Fgiven advice about leaving him and was
OL,12,Ftold to telephone 101.
OL,14,FBethany called the police again four
OL,15,Fdays later to report further threats
OL,16,Fand gave a statement to the police
OL,17,Fthree days after that.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G14/19
