OL,6,FThe domestic homicide review
OL,7,Fidentified a series of failings on the
OL,8,Fpart of West Yorkshire Police in
OL,9,Fidentifying and addressing the risks
OL,10,Fposed to Bethany.
OL,12,FPauline Jones says Bethany was "100%"
OL,13,Ffailed by the authorities.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G16/19
