OL,6,FShe told the review: "Bethany's life
OL,7,Fended needlessly, cruelly without
OL,8,Fjustification, cause or reason other
OL,9,Fthan gross failings, neglect, lack of
OL,10,Fduty of care, absolute lack of
OL,11,Fresponsibility to protect the public,
OL,12,Fespecially known victims of domestic
OL,13,Fabuse."
OL,15,FWest Yorkshire Police said it had
OL,16,Fchanged its approach to domestic abuse
OL,17,Fsince Bethany's death.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G17/19
